reviews.text:
Just mixed a 30ml of this and the aroma and taste test I did was simply amazing &#xD;
right off the shake! I was impressed I tend not to care for anything until at least 3 to 5 days anyways I mixed mine with a little less cap SS as 1% seemed like it would be too sweet for my liking. I'm still going to let this steep for suggested 3 days before filling tanks and will add stars once it's been given it's fair tasting.&#xD;
&#xD;
Update: This is super tasty!! Only thing I may do differently is drop down the cap super sweet next time I mix this to about .5% I feel at 1% it takes away from the profile a little bit other then that though this is an amazing ADV mix! Ty slushy!
